examples.en: He was overdue for a shave.
Her baby is two weeks overdue.
She reminded him that the rent was overdue.
Reform of the law is long overdue.
The move to a larger office building is long overdue.
We welcome this announcement and think it's long overdue.
The loan shark usually imposed a mulct of an additional 20% on overdue payments.
Her boyfriend's articulation of his feelings for her was long overdue.
The baby was a week overdue (=it was expected to be born a week ago).
The librarian told us a lot of hogwash about how you can go to jail for having overdue books.
